MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Goblin
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 39
  mythName: Goblin
  omens:
  - '1. Weeping huntsman, cursing everyone.

    Looking for his lost bloodhound
    who

    tended to him during injury.'
  - '2. A lost lad, full of stories. Claims a little old

    man called him into
    the woods.'
  - '3. Oppressive branches, tripping roots. A

    cloaked old man calls out, lost.
    If alerted

    he cries out just before he is dragged into

    the ground,
    taken to the lost realm.'
  - '4. The lost pets are running wild. If spotted

    they immediately run back
    toward the

    secret door to the lost realm. One drops a

    strange metallic
    bone, repellent to birds.'
  - '5. A dark clearing. Any deals made here are

    bound by fate. The Goblin offers
    a trade.

    A valuable lost thing in return for a

    favour he can call in
    later.'
  - '6. Suddenly dragged to the realm of lost

    things. Tunnels under piles of
    bric-a-brac.

    The Goblin gloats from atop his pile.

    Freedom is only
    granted for a binding

    favour, which the Goblin will enforce.'
  verse: 'On toes it crept just out o'' sight

    The petty hoarder full o'' spite'
  castEntries:
  - name: Lord of all Lost Things
    statBlock: 'VIG 7, CLA 16, SPI 15, 9 GD

      Bony needle (d6 +d10 to anybody
      indebted to'
    notes: 'the wielder), sack of favourite lost things

      Can only be harmed
      by objects that have

      lain lost for at least ninety-nine years.

      Can
      Focus.'
  - name: Lost Pets
    statBlock: 'VIG 5, CLA 10, SPI 5, 2 GD

      Yapping, biting, and scratching
      (d6)'
    notes: 
  - name: Lost Lad, Roth
    statBlock: 'VIG 7, CLA 9, SPI 9, 3 GD

      Practice bow (d4, long)'
    notes: 
  flavorTable:
    title: TRADING THE LOST
    columns:
    - header: Selling
      values:
      - Keys
      - Letters
      - Rings
      - Memories
      - Birds
      - Scarves
    - header: Seeking
      values:
      - Silver
      - Dogs
      - Needles
      - Hats
      - Knives
      - Shoes
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
